item.content:encoded:
Maa Vaishno Devi Inter College one the best school for your children’s learning place. We offer various type of the activities as Sport, Cultural program, Art workshop etc. during learning period so that your child learn more than a basic education. Our faculty one of the best faculty for the modern education.

Our approach to give your child a quality education and skills so they can qualify all kind of the competition.

  • Recognized by Indian Nursing Council, New Delhi
  • Affiliated to MP Nurses Registration Council, Bhopal
  • Affiliated to Madhya Pradesh Medical Science University, Jabalpur
  • Affiliated to Directorate of Medical Education, Government of Madhya Pradesh
